Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.44,0:00:02.69,Default,B,0,0,0,,Mage!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.98,0:00:04.38,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,I'm sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.38,0:00:07.60,Default,WK,0,0,0,,This is one of the legendary heroes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.60,0:00:09.19,Default,B,0,0,0,,What are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.38,0:00:11.70,Default,B,0,0,0,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.70,0:00:12.64,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,Sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.64,0:00:14.16,Default,B,0,0,0,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.16,0:00:16.20,Default,B,0,0,0,,Did you meet the Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.38,0:00:17.50,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.50,0:00:18.50,Default,B,0,0,0,,What was he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:21.45,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,Going to the Demon Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.88,0:00:23.48,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,But more importantly, the Demo—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.14,0:00:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have orders from the Crimson Scholar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.12,0:00:28.20,Default,WK,0,0,0,,Orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.20,0:00:30.24,Default,WK,0,0,0,,You know the Scholar?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.24,0:00:31.42,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,she doesn't know the war's started.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:37.08,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,As such, this may not do you any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:39.51,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,But I'll tell you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.90,0:00:42.16,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,With livestock of the Artiodactyla order,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.16,0:00:44.98,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,one can deliberately infect patients with an attenuated,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.98,0:00:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and thus less dangerous version of the virus,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.84,0:00:51.44,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,resulting in an induced immunity to all related forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.44,0:00:55.98,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,Develop a method, then find a way to instruct and inoculate the populace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.98,0:00:58.87,Default,WK,0,0,0,,Could you perhaps explain that more simply?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.30,0:01:01.16,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,Exterminate smallpox.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:04.12,Default,MS,0,0,0,,Is that even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:07.79,Default,B,0,0,0,,That accursed disease kills three million a year!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.30,0:01:11.96,Default,B,0,0,0,,It's so serious that any house with one smallpox infection is burned to the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.40,0:01:13.80,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,But it {\i1}is{\i0} possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.00,0:01:15.96,Default,B,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.08,0:01:18.97,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,This contains the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:21.74,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,Once you recover, you won't catch it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.74,0:01:23.24,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,Take advantage of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.24,0:01:24.89,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,It works for seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.18,0:01:27.64,Default,WK,0,0,0,,This is hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.64,0:01:29.70,Default,WK,0,0,0,,But if this is what the Scholar says...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.70,0:01:30.82,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,If...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.16,0:01:34.28,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,If all Southern Triad citizens and their allies
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:37.24,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,could receive such treatment for one gold piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:40.70,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,that'd be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:44.16,Default,WK,0,0,0,,I see now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.64,0:01:47.21,Default,WK,0,0,0,,This could change everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.20,0:01:50.00,Default,WK,0,0,0,,We could work for a ceasefire!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:54.01,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,And I'm a demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.58,0:01:56.74,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:05.89,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,I'm sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.89,0:02:09.84,Default,B,0,0,0,,The demons brought a cure for smallpox?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.84,0:02:11.52,Default,B,0,0,0,,Is that what you want us to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:15.53,Default,WK,0,0,0,,You want to bridge the gap between humans and demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.68,0:02:16.74,Default,WK,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.26,0:02:20.03,Default,B,0,0,0,,I'm tired of silly nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:25.08,Default,B,0,0,0,,Sleep should bring good dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.96,0:02:28.04,Default,MS,0,0,0,,It's true that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.26,0:02:31.56,Default,MS,0,0,0,,demons are large and strange to look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.56,0:02:33.92,Default,MS,0,0,0,,But they're intelligent beings who're capable of language.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.74,0:02:37.38,Default,MS,0,0,0,,Just as there are many human nations,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:41.34,Default,MS,0,0,0,,perhaps the Demon Realm has many countries and factions, as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:43.14,Default,MS,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.38,0:02:46.62,Default,DP,0,0,0,,{\i0}If you like, you may take me prisoner.{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.30,0:02:50.12,Default,DP,0,0,0,,{\i0}But please consider my request.{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:54.38,Default,MS,0,0,0,,Please consider her request!
