Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:01.95,Default,Ms,0,0,0,,I hope we don't have a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.36,0:03:03.80,Default,Mb,0,0,0,,Let us believe
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:07.20,Default,Mb,0,0,0,,in the words the Hero sent from the Winter Country.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.74,0:03:09.98,Default,Mb,0,0,0,,Just hold out until snowfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:11.62,Default,Mb,0,0,0,,If the fighting stops,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:13.90,Default,Mb,0,0,0,,then there'll hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:22.30,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,A girl from the Winter Kingdom who wields a strange machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.62,0:03:24.28,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,You must be her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:26.26,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,I've found you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:28.39,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,Crimson Scholar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:30.44,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Come back to me, Demon King!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:34.06,Default,Y,0,0,0,,You said you were just getting your license renewed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:36.23,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Don't sacrifice yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:39.65,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Because you decided on self-sacrifice,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:44.10,Default,Y,0,0,0,,the maid, your double, has become a real saint!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:55.92,Default,M,0,0,0,,You will be mine, Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:57.26,Default,Y,0,0,0,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.26,0:04:00.98,Default,M,0,0,0,,If you join me, I will give you half the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.98,0:04:02.09,Default,Y,0,0,0,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:04.39,Default,M,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:07.56,Default,Y,0,0,0,,You're behind the times, Demon King!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:09.97,Default,Y,0,0,0,,The world doesn't belong to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.42,0:04:13.22,Default,Y,0,0,0,,So it isn't yours to give!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:16.02,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Furthermore...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:19.15,Default,Y,0,0,0,,This body belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:21.53,Default,Y,0,0,0,,You can corrupt it or take it over,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:24.32,Default,Y,0,0,0,,but it's still mine alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the most important thing in the world to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:29.04,Default,M,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:31.58,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Just wake up already,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.40,0:04:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,my Demon King.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:38.59,Default,M,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:40.22,Default,M,0,0,0,,Shut up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:42.55,Default,M,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:47.55,Default,M,0,0,0,,Don't ruin my sweet reunion!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:04:59.94,Default,Y,0,0,0,,You call this sweet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:02.38,Default,Y,0,0,0,,You greedy Demon King.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:07.95,Default,M,0,0,0,,I'm back, my Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:10.18,Default,Y,0,0,0,,You sleep too much,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:12.38,Default,Y,0,0,0,,my Demon King.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:26.09,Default,Mb,0,0,0,,Release my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:28.93,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,Then kneel, heretic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:30.97,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,Apologize to the Holy Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.40,0:05:33.96,Default,Mb,0,0,0,,I believe in the Holy Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:36.02,Default,Mb,0,0,0,,Kneeling means nothing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:41.15,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,How dare you speak the Holy Light's name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:43.30,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,Beg for forgiveness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:46.99,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,Confess your sins and shed tears of humiliation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:50.41,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,Behold, Scholar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:53.46,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,This sword has shed sufficient blood
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.46,0:05:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to be worthy of your name, "Crimson."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:59.56,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,You will be judged by this blade
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:03.71,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,and descend into the red-black hell within my eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.66,0:06:09.14,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:13.35,Default,MS,0,0,0,,Just a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:29.36,Default,M,0,0,0,,Did it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:30.46,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.46,0:06:31.95,Default,Y,0,0,0,,I doubt there'll even be a scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:33.70,Default,M,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:39.46,Default,Y,0,0,0,,There's a lot happening back on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:41.71,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Where do we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:43.46,Default,M,0,0,0,,Wherever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:45.90,Default,M,0,0,0,,Tell me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.06,0:06:51.30,Default,Merc,0,0,0,,Tasteless bean soup and stale bread crusts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:54.35,Default,Merc,0,0,0,,I'd heard that grain prices had risen, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:58.34,Default,Merc2,0,0,0,,I guess the army brought a lot of money,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.34,0:07:01.15,Default,Merc2,0,0,0,,but barely any food.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:02.62,Default,Merc,0,0,0,,Why not bring food?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.24,0:07:05.02,Default,Merc3,0,0,0,,Can't you guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:08.78,Default,Merc3,0,0,0,,Money is easier to transport
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:10.91,Default,Merc3,0,0,0,,and more efficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:13.64,Default,Merc3,0,0,0,,But the nobles are starting to panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.64,0:07:17.83,Default,Merc3,0,0,0,,Money's great, but without food, you'll starve in winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:21.54,Default,Merc3,0,0,0,,That's why they began a war with the Southern Triad,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,which still has food.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:25.80,Default,Merc2,0,0,0,,So why aren't we attacking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:27.55,Default,Merc,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:31.20,Default,Merc2,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:34.35,Default,Merc,0,0,0,,And also, they're arguing at Command HQ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,over who receives the southern territories, once they've fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:40.14,Default,Merc2,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:41.48,Default,Merc2,0,0,0,,Fuck that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:42.82,Default,Merc,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.82,0:07:45.02,Default,Merc,0,0,0,,The High Priest is here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:47.53,Default,Merc,0,0,0,,He'll settle things with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:49.60,Default,Merc,0,0,0,,So you're saying
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.60,0:07:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,everything we've been through is some test by the Holy Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.14,0:07:53.82,Default,Merc,0,0,0,,You're all a bunch of idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.88,0:07:55.53,Default,General,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:58.08,Default,General,0,0,0,,They still haven't decided when to start the war!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.34,0:08:01.54,Default,Soldiers,0,0,0,,Well, a few of the mercenaries have attacked on their own...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:02.75,Default,General,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.38,0:08:04.98,Default,General,0,0,0,,We must mount an immediate defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:06.42,Default,K,0,0,0,,There's no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.72,0:08:09.30,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'll head out at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:10.44,Default,WK,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:12.32,Default,K,0,0,0,,If the battle is prolonged,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll hand 20,000 Central soldiers the excuse they need to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.98,Default,K,0,0,0,,We attack right away with our best equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:20.78,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:23.73,Default,WK,0,0,0,,Fewer than 200 have that good of equipment!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:26.30,Default,K,0,0,0,,At most, they number a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:28.58,Default,K,0,0,0,,This doesn't even qualify as a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:34.41,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I can't let a real one begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.72,0:08:36.56,Default,K,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:56.05,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,What's wrong, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:09:00.01,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,There are some things you can't protect, no matter how much you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.32,0:09:01.64,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,Give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:03.64,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,This is reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:10.82,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:13.14,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,How can you block with your wrists?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:20.24,Default,MS,0,0,0,,I wrapped steel arrows around my wrists to protect my forearms.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.82,0:09:24.71,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,Your tricks won't save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:34.92,Default,Ms,0,0,0,,Soldier! {i-yaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:43.06,Default,K,0,0,15,,We strike once, then withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:45.23,Default,K,0,0,15,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:54.13,Default,K,0,0,0,,Don't try to be a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:02.45,Default,Mercenary,0,0,0,,They've turned around!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:03.45,Default,Mercenary,0,0,0,,Behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:04.91,Default,Mercenary,0,0,0,,On the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:06.14,Default,Mercenary,0,0,0,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:07.44,Default,Mercenary,0,0,0,,I can't see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:09.25,Default,K,0,0,0,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.62,0:10:19.43,Default,K,0,0,0,,Pull back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:21.22,Default,K,0,0,0,,Form ranks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:22.78,Default,K,0,0,0,,Formation 16!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:24.70,Default,Mercs,0,0,0,,After them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:25.85,Default,Mercs,0,0,0,,They aren't many.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:27.52,Default,Mercs,0,0,0,,But Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:29.60,Default,Mercs,0,0,0,,The horses are tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:30.65,Default,Mercs,0,0,0,,We can't keep this up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:31.80,Default,Mercs,0,0,0,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:33.40,Default,Mercs,0,0,0,,Just a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.70,0:10:36.94,Default,Mercs,0,0,0,,They split up their ranks?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:39.18,Default,Mercs,0,0,0,,Which way do we pursue?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:41.38,Default,Mercs,0,0,0,,You take the right side!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:43.66,Default,Mercs,0,0,0,,I'll take the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:46.12,Default,Mercs,0,0,0,,Once we catch up, they're ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:55.88,Default,Mercs,0,0,0,,They split up again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:58.34,Default,Mercs,0,0,0,,Wh-Which way do we follow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:10:59.51,Default,Mercs,0,0,0,,Both!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:01.30,Default,Mercs,0,0,0,,Chase both!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:06.10,Default,General,0,0,0,,They're following us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.26,0:11:07.10,Default,K,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:08.52,Default,K,0,0,0,,We'll head to the rendezvous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:11.20,Default,K,0,0,0,,We've split them enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:23.00,Default,Ms,0,0,0,,Where's Soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:24.66,Default,Ss,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.22,0:11:34.60,Default,General,0,0,0,,Everyone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.60,0:11:37.74,Default,General,0,0,0,,A few are lightly wounded, but all are accounted for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:38.64,Default,K,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:41.97,Default,K,0,0,0,,We reform as one, then attack again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:44.89,Default,K,0,0,0,,But this time, just unseat them from their horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:47.72,Default,K,0,0,0,,It isn't for us to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:49.77,Default,K,0,0,0,,They, too, are the Holy Light's disciples.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:53.42,Default,K,0,0,0,,We oppose each other now, but we are brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:03.80,Default,K,0,0,0,,It came.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:05.95,Default,General,0,0,0,,Reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:07.38,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.38,0:12:09.00,Default,K,0,0,0,,the strongest we could hope for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:15.29,Default,SomeGuy,0,0,0,,And you claim to be the Demon Realm's mightiest army?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:18.80,Default,SomeGuy,0,0,0,,You couldn't even make it across the snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.02,0:12:23.06,Default,BlueGuy,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear that from cowards who ran without putting up a fight
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.06,0:12:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,because they lacked food.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.88,0:12:27.26,Default,SomeGuy,0,0,0,,You babysit the Prince, so don't take that tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.46,0:12:29.01,Default,BlueGuy,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:34.14,Default,Pope,0,0,0,,Silence, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:37.50,Default,Pope,0,0,0,,This went just as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:40.61,Default,Pope,0,0,0,,The Alliance caused the rise in prices.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:44.11,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Those accursed merchants have no plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:47.70,Default,RealImportantGuy,0,0,0,,When our goal has been reached, you will have
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the Southern Triad's territory as promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:53.91,Default,RealImportantGuy,0,0,0,,Rule it as you see fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:58.34,Default,BlueGuy,0,0,0,,We will forever play the church's enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:03.34,Default,BlueGuy,0,0,0,,to make certain that you will always rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:08.14,Default,Pope,0,0,0,,The church must always be united.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.34,0:13:09.64,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And to ensure this, I shall raise a Third Crusade of the Holy Key.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:16.82,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,It will destroy the Southern Triad,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,recapture Gate City, and even slay the Demon King.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:24.58,Default,OtherGuy2,0,0,0,,But the Demon Realm is huge. How can you conquer it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.58,0:13:26.41,Default,RealImportantGuy,0,0,0,,We have a secret weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:28.07,Default,OtherGuy2,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:32.66,Default,RIG,0,0,0,,It uses black powder to propel projectiles that pierce the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:34.83,Default,RIG,0,0,0,,That heretic,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:37.46,Default,RIG,0,0,0,,the Crimson Scholar, hired someone
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Iron Country to develop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:43.04,Default,RIG,0,0,0,,Mass produce it, and even an army of slaves
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,will be several times more powerful than what we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:49.64,Default,Pope,0,0,0,,I hear a voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:51.60,Default,Priest,0,0,0,,Tell us its words!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:55.22,Default,Pope,0,0,0,,Obtain the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.18,0:13:59.35,Default,Pope,0,0,0,,The Demon King's life...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.74,0:14:02.86,Default,Pope,0,0,0,,The desire of the church...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:07.18,Default,Pope,0,0,0,,The bones of the Light Spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:10.80,Default,Pope,0,0,0,,Attain them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.52,0:14:14.58,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,Hey, master.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:17.56,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,There's nothing out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.30,0:14:19.33,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,There is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.02,0:14:21.34,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,Dispelling invisibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.20,0:14:26.76,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:28.58,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,The spatial density is incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.58,0:14:32.02,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,I feel the power of a strange spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:35.14,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,The spell creates a high-density pillar of force.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:38.27,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,Magic from the age of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:43.15,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,This is a liquefied magic circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:46.66,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,I'm a fake, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:50.92,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,It's crazy to think I could be the original, no matter how hard I try.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:56.16,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,If you and the Hero are the ones to see the result, that will suffice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.92,0:14:59.67,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,I shall remain the spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:01.92,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm redundant?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:12.64,Default,Y,0,0,0,,The Demon King's really popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:15.12,Default,HM,0,0,0,,Not at all, compared to previous ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:18.40,Default,HM,0,0,0,,In the Demon Realm, the more you excel at fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the more you are respected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.22,0:15:24.20,Default,HM,0,0,0,,If she were the previous Demon King, at least a hundred would've fainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.20,0:15:26.02,Default,M,0,0,0,,My comrades...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.54,0:15:28.00,Default,M,0,0,0,,My people!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:32.03,Default,M,0,0,0,,As you can see, I am well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:34.14,Default,M,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I am glad that you all have also endured these harsh days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.36,0:15:41.37,Default,M,0,0,0,,I have returned
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:43.12,Default,M,0,0,0,,to the Demon Realm!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:46.80,Default,HM,0,0,0,,That sounds like your cue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:48.38,Default,Y,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:53.80,Default,M,0,0,0,,I am glad to see that Gate City was retaken in my absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:59.56,Default,M,0,0,0,,That city will remain under my direct control and protection!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.38,0:16:05.64,Default,M,0,0,0,,And my loyal sword and general, the Dark Knight,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.64,0:16:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,has punished those who rebelled against me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and broke my laws!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:27.84,Default,HM,0,0,0,,Flashier!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:29.38,Default,HM,0,0,0,,Flashy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:32.13,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Huh? Flashy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.79,0:16:34.72,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Plasma Annihilator.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:01.88,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Whoops. I overdid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:10.72,Default,M,0,0,0,,It's been 20 years since first contact with humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.72,0:17:14.14,Default,M,0,0,0,,We've now come to the crossroads of our destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:16.93,Default,M,0,0,0,,And now I
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:22.10,Default,M,0,0,0,,call for a meeting of all the Greater Races, a Quriltai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:23.36,Default,Demons,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:25.56,Default,Demons,0,0,0,,The day has finally come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:28.19,Default,Demons,0,0,0,,Full-scale war with the humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:31.19,Default,Demons,0,0,0,,This time, we will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:33.82,Default,M,0,0,0,,No! That isn't what I wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:37.08,Default,M,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:38.12,Default,M,0,0,0,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:42.24,Default,M,0,0,0,,At the Quriltai, the chiefs of each of the races will decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:44.96,Default,M,0,0,0,,Spread word to the entire Demon Realm
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.34,0:17:48.42,Default,M,0,0,0,,that their King now summons them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.32,0:17:56.46,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:18:00.98,Default,M,0,0,0,,There's still a lot of work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:02.01,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:05.93,Default,Y,0,0,0,,I'll be with you the whole time, no matter how long it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.66,0:18:09.06,Default,M,0,0,0,,Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:12.07,Default,Demons,0,0,0,,Demon King! {might wanna combine this and the next two into 1 line with "Demon King! repeated 3 times}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:14.28,Default,Demons,0,0,0,,Demon King!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:16.70,Default,Demons,0,0,0,,Demon King!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.28,0:18:28.52,Default,Mb,0,0,0,,The Southern Triad's potatoes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.52,0:18:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,were sold to the Central Nations via the Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.60,0:18:34.00,Default,Mb,0,0,0,,If they can taste them
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:37.76,Default,Mb,0,0,0,,and realize for themselves that they aren't a demon fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:43.26,Default,Mb,0,0,0,,it's possible that several countries may lean toward the south, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.66,0:18:46.52,Default,M,0,0,0,,It's the first step toward a dual-currency system.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:49.10,Default,M,0,0,0,,And a more mature economy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.62,0:18:52.81,Default,Mb,0,0,0,,What surprised me were the words from the man of the Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.26,0:18:57.50,Default,YM,0,0,0,,{\i0}I'd like you to agree to immediately end hostilities against demons,{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.50,0:19:00.99,Default,YM,0,0,0,,{\i0}as well as allow the Alliance to trade with them.{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:03.18,Default,Iron King,0,0,0,,{\i0}Trade with the demons? Impossible!{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:04.32,Default,YM,0,0,0,,{\i0}I can do it.{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.38,0:19:08.37,Default,YM,0,0,0,,{\i0}I propose this as a merchant.{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.30,0:19:11.37,Default,YM,0,0,0,,{\i0}I'm willing to bet my life on it.{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:15.67,Default,WK,0,0,0,,{\i0}I can't give you an answer right now.{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.16,0:19:22.26,Default,WK,0,0,0,,{\i0}But I wish to hear more about the demons.{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.46,0:19:27.64,Default,WK,0,0,0,,{\i0}It's possible that both worlds are more similar than we believe.{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:32.73,Default,Mb,0,0,0,,He said, "Right now, that is how I feel."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:38.28,Default,M,0,0,0,,So what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.62,0:19:40.95,Default,K,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:42.72,Default,K,0,0,0,,Basically...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.72,0:19:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,While you were gone, I gave it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.66,0:19:49.75,Default,M,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:52.25,Default,K,0,0,0,,M-M-My sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:54.22,Default,K,0,0,0,,Not my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.22,0:19:55.67,Default,M,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.04,0:19:58.10,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I did it while you were away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:01.05,Default,K,0,0,0,,I may have forced him into it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:03.26,Default,M,0,0,0,,Why are you telling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:05.55,Default,K,0,0,0,,Because you belong to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:08.42,Default,K,0,0,0,,That's part of it, but mostly...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.44,0:20:12.06,Default,K,0,0,0,,Because you said you were my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:15.23,Default,K,0,0,0,,I don't want to come between you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:18.06,Default,K,0,0,0,,Even if Hero never touches me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.06,0:20:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can live with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.26,0:20:24.42,Default,M,0,0,0,,I'm sure the Hero would prefer a human girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:29.33,Default,M,0,0,0,,Part of me still feels that, and it saddens me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:30.70,Default,K,0,0,0,,Demon King...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:33.12,Default,M,0,0,0,,But I love the Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:35.76,Default,M,0,0,0,,As my owner...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:37.71,Default,M,0,0,0,,As a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:40.71,Default,K,0,0,0,,I love him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:43.74,Default,K,0,0,0,,As the master of my blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:45.09,Default,K,0,0,0,,And as a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:46.05,OP,,0,0,0,,{OP}{First white frame}
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.02,0:21:00.98,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}I want to be annoying for you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.98,0:21:03.95,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}I don't mind being conceited
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.95,0:21:07.99,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Hide a tree in a forest, they say
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.74,0:21:12.50,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}It started with a little mistake
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.50,0:21:15.50,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Let's redo our meeting from there
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.50,0:21:19.96,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Let's oppose the strand of time
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.71,0:21:25.93,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Strength alone is no weapon
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.01,0:21:34.10,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}You taught me that just now
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.10,0:21:39.61,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}I want to show you what lies
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.61,0:21:45.82,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}beyond these days
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.82,0:21:48.37,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}The wind is strong
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.37,0:21:51.45,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}I'm sure you know that too
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.45,0:21:56.29,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}I can't fly
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.29,0:22:03.09,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Sharing makes you dependant
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.09,0:22:06.26,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Now, take my hand
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.26,0:22:08.80,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Hold it tight
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.80,0:22:13.10,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.00,0:22:31.07,Default,M,0,0,0,,I never expected the seeds I sowed to bloom like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.28,0:22:31.98,Default,HM,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.48,0:22:34.58,Default,M,0,0,0,,Her, more than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.58,0:22:38.21,Default,M,0,0,0,,This, and this alone, wasn't something I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.25,0:22:42.92,Default,M,0,0,0,,It's the beginning of liberalism,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,born of her wounds, pain, and blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.12,0:22:47.88,Default,HM,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.58,0:22:50.39,Default,M,0,0,0,,Aren't you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.02,0:22:54.89,Default,HM,0,0,0,,How much could I really do for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.58,0:22:59.31,Default,M,0,0,0,,Humans amaze me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.60,0:23:02.90,Default,M,0,0,0,,Their world is so boisterous and chaotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.90,0:23:04.82,Default,M,0,0,0,,But I love it more than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.32,0:23:10.24,Default,HM,0,0,0,,Are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.48,0:23:13.84,Default,M,0,0,0,,I don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.94,0:23:15.90,Default,M,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.76,0:23:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.32,0:23:22.46,Default,M,0,0,0,,Not that it was my doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.06,0:23:25.64,Default,HM,0,0,0,,I'm glad
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.64,0:23:26.90,Default,HM,0,0,0,,you two met.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.90,0:23:27.68,Default,M,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.12,0:23:30.38,Default,M,0,0,0,,I love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.12,0:23:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.30,0:23:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,